def_cn: （想法、愿望、感情）没有言明的，没有说出口的
def_en: If your thoughts, wishes, or feelings are unspoken, you do not speak about them.

def_cn: （协议等）不成文的，默契的，默认的
def_en: When there is an unspoken agreement or understanding between people, their behaviour shows that they agree about something or understand it, even though they have never spoken about it.
